вҠў greet
  given name
  yield message

  вҲҙ Greet the person called В«nameВ» with a warm,
    friendly hello. One sentence only.

  вҠЁ message contains В«nameВ»
  вҠЁ message is exactly one sentence

вҠў wrap
  given greetвҶ’message
  yield text, emoji

  вҲҙ Take В«greetвҶ’messageВ» and pass it through unchanged
    as text. Choose a single emoji that fits the mood
    of the greeting.

  вҠЁ text = В«greetвҶ’messageВ»
  вҠЁ emoji is a single unicode emoji character
